                                <span class="tei-persName">Pelagia</span>
                                was a martyr.
                             <a href="/3141-8" class="factoid-more"> See factoid page <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p><p class="indent"><span class="spearLabel">sanctity: </span><span class="tei-persName">Mare</span> was a martyr. <a href="/805-84" class="factoid-more"> See factoid page <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p><p class="indent"><span class="spearLabel">sanctity: </span>
